Package de.jcommandlineparser

Interface Summary
CmdLineParser An implementation of CmdLineParser will provide command line argument parsing functionality.
Strategy The Strategy interface represents a parsing strategy, meaning the parsing logic.
 

Class Summary
AbstractOption<T> An implementation of AbstractOption represents an program option, for that the command line string is parsed for.
BooleanOption BooleanOption represents an program option of type boolean.
CharacterOption CharacterOption represents an program option of type character.
CmdLineParserImpl Highly flexible command line option parser.
DoubleOption DoubleOption represents an program option of type double.
FileOption FileOption represents an program option of type File.
IntegerOption IntegerOption represents an program option of type integer.
LongOption LongOption represents an program option of type long.
OptionBuilder This class provides static factory methods for creating program options.
StringOption StringOption represents an program option of type string.
Test Example use of ComdLineParser
VoidOption VoidOption represents an program option of type void.
